                            <comment id="13406284" author="cheolsoo" created="Wed, 4 Jul 2012 06:34:26 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is the patch that replaces obsolete sort options with posix options in e2e tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Modified tests are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Checkin, Foreach, Order, Types, Limit, Split, MissingColumns, Jython_Checkin, and BigData&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I verified that all tests pass in local mode.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13409814" author="daijy" created="Mon, 9 Jul 2012 21:28:52 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to trunk. Thanks Cheolsoo!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
